OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783675170
OL,3,CMan accused of attack which sparked
OL,4,Crace riots told case moving to crown
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FA man accused of attempted murder in
OL,8,Fnorth Belfast has been told his case
OL,9,Fwill be going to the Crown Court.
OL,11,FHadi Alodid, 30, of Duncairn Avenue in
OL,12,FBelfast, appeared before the city's
OL,13,Fmagistrates' court by videolink on
OL,14,FWednesday.
OL,16,FHe is charged with the attempted
OL,17,Fmurder of Stephen Ogilvie, who the
OL,18,Fcourt previously heard lost his left
OL,19,Feye and received deep cuts to his
OL,20,Fhead, face and back.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
