PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783675170
OL,3,CMan accused of attack which sparked
OL,4,Crace riots told case moving to crown
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FThe PSNI said earlier this week that
OL,8,FAlodid may be from Chad, and not Sudan
OL,9,Fas previously believed.
OL,11,FHe has also been charged with
OL,12,Fthreatening to kill an NHS
OL,13,Fradiographer and with possession of a
OL,14,Fknife.
OL,16,FThe incident sparked a wave of race
OL,17,Friots in parts of Northern Ireland,
OL,18,Fwhich led to widespread disruption.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
