PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783675170
OL,3,CMan accused of attack which sparked
OL,4,Crace riots told case moving to crown
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FOn Wednesday, the court heard requests
OL,8,Ffor outstanding evidence including
OL,9,Fstatements and medical evidence had
OL,10,Fbeen made.
OL,12,FA request to move the proceedings back
OL,13,Ffour weeks awaiting those materials
OL,14,Fwas granted.
OL,16,FThe magistrate told Alodid, who was
OL,17,Fusing an Arabic interpreter, he is
OL,18,Ffacing serious charges and he should
OL,19,Fconsider seeking legal representation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
