PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783675170
OL,3,CMan accused of attack which sparked
OL,4,Crace riots told case moving to crown
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FHe was told his case will be going to
OL,8,Fthe Crown Court and it is hoped a date
OL,9,Ffor that process to happen would be
OL,10,Ffixed in four weeks' time.
OL,12,FThe accused shook his head when asked,
OL,13,Fthrough the interpreter, if he had
OL,14,Fanything to say in response.
OL,16,FAlodid was remanded in custody until
OL,17,FAugust 5.
